@startuml pattern_builder
title Builder Pattern - User and Equipment Construction

class User {
  +getHourlyRate(): double
}
class "User.Builder" as UserBuilder {
  +id(int)
  +name(String)
  +email(String)
  +password(String)
  +userType(UserType)
  +identityNumber(String)
  +department(String)
  +approved(boolean)
  +build(): User
}

class Equipment
class "Equipment.Builder" as EquipmentBuilder {
  +equipmentId(String)
  +name(String)
  +description(String)
  +labLocation(String)
  +status(EquipmentStatus)
  +build(): Equipment
}

class RegisterFrame
class ManagerDashboardFrame

UserBuilder --> User : build()
EquipmentBuilder --> Equipment : build()
RegisterFrame --> UserBuilder : construct user safely
ManagerDashboardFrame --> EquipmentBuilder : construct equipment safely

note right of UserBuilder
Req1, Req8
end note

note right of EquipmentBuilder
Req7
end note

@enduml
